ntical between the original Llama 3 8B and Llama 3.1 8B models — the main difference between the two versions is the RoPE scaling configuration (Llama 3.1 supports a longer context window via `rope_scaling`).\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
